description: The Grilled Cheese Emergency truck is a converted ambulance that can't take you to the hospital, but it can take you back to the good old days when all your bad feelings could be cured by a delicious, hot, gooey cheese sandwich and hearty tomato soup. Planning a special event? The Grilled Cheese emergency truck can rescue you from the trials and tribulations of cooking! Keep an eye out for them on the streets of Chattanooga!
name: The Grilled Cheese Emergency
